{"id": "art-44", "label": "Art. 44", "title": "Art. 44: Sancţiune", "slug": "art-44", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_903509867\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1290\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_903509867\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 44:\nSanc&#355;iune </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_381880905\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1289\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_381880905\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Actele f&#259;cute de persoana lipsit&#259; de\ncapacitate de exerci&#355;iu sau cu capacitate de exerci&#355;iu\nrestrâns&#259;, altele decât cele prev&#259;zute la art. 41 alin. (3) &#351;i\nla art. 43 alin. (3), precum &#351;i actele f&#259;cute de tutore\nf&#259;r&#259; avizul consiliului de familie sau autorizarea instan&#355;ei de\ntutel&#259;, atunci când acestea sunt cerute de lege, sunt anulabile, chiar\nf&#259;r&#259; dovedirea unui prejudiciu.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_139065207\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1288\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_139065207\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Cel lipsit de capacitate de exerci&#355;iu sau cu\ncapacitate de exerci&#355;iu restrâns&#259; poate invoca &#351;i singur, în\nap&#259;rare, anulabilitatea actului pentru înc&#259;lcarea dispozi&#355;iilor\nlegale în materie de capacitate de exerci&#355;iu.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}